articles.title: Trump leaves Alaska summit with Putin empty-handed after failing to reach a deal to end Ukraine war
articles.description: After high-stakes talks in Alaska, Trump says no deal to end the Russia-Ukraine war was made with Putin [2].

articles.title: Flash floods kill hundreds in Pakistan, India
articles.description: Heavy monsoon rains caused flash floods in northern Pakistan, resulting in over 300 deaths [3, 4].

articles.title: Air Canada suspends flights after cabin staff go on strike
articles.description: Air Canada has suspended operations due to a strike by flight attendants [3, 4].
